    "description": "\u003cp\u003eContabo is a fast-growing German server provider serving customers in 178 countries. Our rapid growth is fueled by truly German quality of service and great prices.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eWhere do we need your help\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eYou set the groundbreaking course in close cooperation with the team and actively\nparticipate in the technical conceptual design and solution\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eYou have experience in implementing web front-ends with user experience (UX) methods\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eYou have a good hand for the design (CSS frameworks) and usability of user\ninterfaces (UI)\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eThe technical implementation of user interfaces with Svelte is no problem for you\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eIn addition, you have experience with SPA and possibly PWA\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003c/ul\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eWhat are we looking for\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eYou have a university degree in computer science or comparable training\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eYou have very good knowledge in the area of UX, UI and TypeScript\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eYou are a team player and have an agile mindset\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eFluent English language skills and preferably basic understanding of German\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003c/ul\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eWhat we offer\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eThe opportunity to develop professionally and personally in an innovative and\ntechnological environment\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eConveniently located offices in Munich, Nuremberg or Cologne\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eThe possibility to work in a mobile office\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eFree coffee, drinks, snacks and fruit in the office\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eMany team events like summer party, Christmas party or visit of the oktoberfest\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eOpen communication across all levels and the opportunity to help shape the exciting\ndevelopment of the company\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003c/ul\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://camo.githubusercontent.com/40d7bb8c7cbff27453c56afa2daa5affff0168e1/68747470733a2f2f742e676f686972696e672e636f6d2f682f65633834346639373732653562396562383933663263383931343132666539363466616632373562653962626333613731646136373834316539376139343736\"\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n",
