    "title": "Systems Developer",
    "description": "\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eWe are looking for an experienced developer with a passion for games, development and architecture. Someone who thrives in a changing environment, and works together to solve problems and create scalable solutions.\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eAs systems developer you will be an integral part of our game development teams. You work closely with art and design, and plan systems and tools to bring our game visions to live. You understand what it takes to work in multidisciplinary teams, and strive for improving what and how we develop.\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eRESPONSIBILITIES\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eCreate games together with artist, designers and producers\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eChampion code quality, scalability, stability and performance\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eDesign, develop and iterate on game systems\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eTake ownership in finding technical solutions and estimating new features and projects\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eCollaborate and promote cross-project cooperation and knowledge sharing\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003c/ul\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eROLE-BASED SKILLS\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eWhat we are looking for:\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eExcellent C# programming skills\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eUnderstanding of readable, robust code and best practices\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eUnderstanding of programming patterns\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eUnderstanding of debugging, performance monitoring and optimization\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eThe ability to summarize complex topics both verbally and in writing\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eExperience using source control systems and tools\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003c/ul\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eWhat could help:\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eUnderstanding of game development processes and tools\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eExperience with mobile \u0026amp; console development\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eKnowledge of other programming languages\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eUnderstanding of client / server communication and data serialization\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eExperience with build automation and build scripts\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eExperience with third-party API’s and SDK’s\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eExperience with writing clear, concise and accurate technical documentation\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003c/ul\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eSoft skills:\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cstrong\u003eInsight\u003c/strong\u003e: Deconstructing complex situations in order to obtain and share a complete picture\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cstrong\u003eAccountability\u003c/strong\u003e: Taking responsibility for your own actions and those of your colleagues\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cstrong\u003eFlexibility\u003c/strong\u003e: Adapting to reach a certain goal\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cstrong\u003eInitiative\u003c/strong\u003e: Recognizing and creating opportunities\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003c/ul\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eAre you qualified?\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eWe would much rather read your application, than miss out on a great candidate. So please apply if you are interested!\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eQUALIFICATIONS\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eA strong passion for making games\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e5+ years experience in programming\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e3+ years experience with Unity development with at least 1 game published\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eExcellent English communication skills, both written and verbal\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003c/ul\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eCULTURAL COMPETENCIES\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003ePaladin has five core values that we’re looking for in team members:\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cstrong\u003eKaizen\u003c/strong\u003e: We make positive changes on a regular basis\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cstrong\u003eSpark\u003c/strong\u003e: We leave a mark, providing a positive experience for everyone involved\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cstrong\u003eWholehearted\u003c/strong\u003e: We love the work we do, and we commit to our work\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cstrong\u003eFellowship\u003c/strong\u003e: We are in this together\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cstrong\u003eAutonomy\u003c/strong\u003e: We make decisions and take responsibility for our actions\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003c/ul\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eWE OFFER\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eDiverse and challenging projects\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eA place in a highly motivated and skilled team and an ambitious company\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003ePositive, healthy work environment\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eCoaching and plenty of opportunities for personal development\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eA high degree of freedom and responsibility\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eCompetitive salary and benefits\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003c/ul\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eWe work in autonomous development teams. This ensures tight communications, a real sense of ownership and truly agile development. In our weekly show \u0026amp; tell meetings, every team shares their progress and all aspects of the company can be discussed. We believe in transparency and autonomy, and this creates a high degree of freedom and responsibility.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eABOUT PALADIN STUDIOS\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eWe create games that make people smile – be it a sweet twinkle, loud laugh, or evil grin.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003ePaladin is a game developer. Our basecamp is in The Hague but we are currently working remote due to COVID-19. We are a team of 35+ knights and growing. Our mission is to create games with a spark, for players all over the world. We achieve this goal by being a world-class game studio with soul, that brings out the best in people. That means a studio filled to the brim with creativity, professionalism, and good vibes.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eSome of our recent games include:\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003ca href=\"http:/paladinstudios.com/cut-the-rope\"\u003eCut The Rope Remastered\u003c/a\u003e  - A remaster of the legendary Cut the Rope puzzle game!\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003ca href=\"http:/paladinstudios.com/good-job\"\u003eGood Job!\u003c/a\u003e  - Climb the corporate ladder one office-themed puzzle at a time\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003ca href=\"http:/paladinstudios.com/stormbound\"\u003eStormbound\u003c/a\u003e  – Tactical CCG combat with beautiful visuals\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003ca href=\"http:/paladinstudios.com/tamagotchi\"\u003eMy Tamagotchi Forever\u003c/a\u003e  – The 90s reborn on your smartphone!\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003c/ul\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHOW TO APPLY\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eDoes this sound good? Awesome! To apply, please fill in the \u003ca href=\"https://paladinstudios.bamboohr.com/jobs/view.php?id=48\"\u003eapplication form\u003c/a\u003e . First come, first serve. Please link to your portfolio and CV or add them as attachments.\u003c/p\u003e\n",
    "how_to_apply": "\u003cp\u003ePlease use this link to apply: \u003ca href=\"https://paladinstudios.bamboohr.com/jobs/view.php?id=48\"\u003ehttps://paladinstudios.bamboohr.com/jobs/view.php?id=48\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n",
