    "location": "Berlin",
    "title": "Junior Frontend Developer",
    "description": "<p><strong>At Hybrid Heroes we're looking for a Junior Frontend Developer to help us build outstanding cross platform mobile apps.</strong></p>\n<p>Are you interested in developing next-gen mobile apps? Does bad UX bug the %&amp;§! out of you? Do you know what the terms TypeScript and State Management mean? If you answered check, check and check, then we want you to join our team as a frontend developer and to become a cross platform app development expert!</p>\n<h2>About the job</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>Develop mobile apps using state-of-the-art cross platform frameworks such as React Native or Ionic\nContribute to projects from idea to launch and beyond within an agile environment</li>\n<li>Rise to exciting technical challenges with each new project and solve them with custom-tailored sets of technologies</li>\n<li>Work with a cross functional team of developers, testers and designers</li>\n<li>Be involved and help others, share your knowledge in pair programming sessions, presentations and on our blog</li>\n<li>Have a vote in refining our workflows and technology stack</li>\n</ul>\n<h2>Our tech stack</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>React Native</li>\n<li>Ionic</li>\n<li>Electron</li>\n<li>Redux</li>\n<li>TypeScript</li>\n<li>Flutter</li>\n<li>Docker</li>\n</ul>\n<h2>About you</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>Relevant university degree or a minimum of 2 years of relevant work experience</li>\n<li>You have developed web apps using Angular, React or Vue</li>\n<li>Familiar interfacing with common backend technologies such as REST, GraphQL or Firebase</li>\n<li>Proficient using git and source code hosting services</li>\n<li>Conceptual understanding of technologies such as TypeScript, Redux, Node.js, Docker</li>\n<li>Very good communication skills in English</li>\n</ul>\n<h2>About the company</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>A dynamic, motivated and international team. Our company language is English!</li>\n<li>Flexible working hours</li>\n<li>The freedom to work from home or our modern office in Berlin Schöneberg</li>\n<li>Lively team culture with regular events</li>\n<li>Flat hierarchies and everyday opportunities to learn, grow and develop</li>\n<li>A welcoming onboarding process where you will get to know everybody in the company and ship some code to production within the first day</li>\n</ul>\n<h2>Apply for the job</h2>\n<p>Do you want to join our team as our new Junior Frontend Developer? Then we'd love to hear about you!</p>\n",
