    "location": "Berlin",
    "title": "Senior Frontend Developer (m/w/d)",
    "description": "<p>At Carl we support owners of small and medium-sized companies on their way to a successful company sale. Platform-based technology solutions provide our customers with uncomplicated access to a unique buyer network. Carl offers customized options to medium-sized businesses that for a long time were only available to large corporations. We promise our customers a company transfer with a high probability of success, in which the wishes of the entrepreneur are always at the forefront.</p>\n<p>Carl is currently actively involved in over 30 transactions with a combined volume of more than EUR 240 million. The team has gathered meaningful experience in leading companies (J.P. Morgan, McKinsey, Rocket Internet, Google etc.) and is supported by prominent advisory boards and investors. We address a fundamental problem of the European economy and pursue the goal of digitizing and professionalizing business succession in medium-sized companies. Initiative and commitment are rewarded with extensive responsibility in this phase of company development. If you are enthusiastic about this vision and would like to actively support the digitization of medium-sized businesses, we look forward to hearing from you!</p>\n<p><strong>Responsibilities</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Primarily focus on building up the new Carl platform</li>\n<li>Be part of our multicultural team and strive to build products that delight users</li>\n<li>Provide guidance and mentorship to more junior developers</li>\n<li>Work with the product team to define and realise the product roadmap</li>\n</ul>\n<p><em>Work with a modern technology stack. Some examples of tools that we use are:</em></p>\n<ul>\n<li>React, NextJS</li>\n<li>Chakra UI, TailwindCSS</li>\n<li>Formik, react-intl</li>\n<li>Zustand for state management</li>\n<li>Webpack, Lerna</li>\n<li>Maintain our existing applications</li>\n</ul>\n<p><em>Work on the Carl shared libraries. We have libraries for:</em></p>\n<ul>\n<li>UI elements</li>\n<li>Data fetching + storage</li>\n<li>Analytics</li>\n<li>and more...</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Requirements</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>More than 5-7 years of professional experience as a frontend developer</li>\n<li>Very good experience in working with the React ecosystem in larger projects</li>\n<li>You have experience in the complete feature lifecycle - from conception to final launch</li>\n<li>Are proactive in coming up with solutions to challenges</li>\n<li>Happy to take ownership of the technical side of the product</li>\n<li>You have experience mentoring other developers</li>\n<li>You can speak English fluently (German is a plus)</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Benefits</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Possibility to shape an entire industry with the help of software</li>\n<li>Challenging tasks, high responsibility, and a high impact</li>\n<li>Responsibility for own projects and a steep learning curve</li>\n<li>Working closely with an experienced developer team</li>\n<li>Deep insight into the workflow in a fast-growing startup</li>\n<li>Flat hierarchies as well as short and direct communication channels</li>\n<li>Motivated, talented colleagues</li>\n<li>Gym membership and other employer benefits</li>\n<li>Great atmosphere with free fruits &amp; drinks in our office in Berlin-Mitte</li>\n</ul>\n",
    "how_to_apply": "<p><a href=\"https://carl.join.com/jobs/2049948-senior-frontend-developer-m-w-d?pid=357a3b4531918760973f&amp;oid=931a7239-ba3b-4e08-bcd1-ce4c27baa804&amp;utm_source=github_jobs&amp;utm_medium=paid&amp;utm_campaign=single%2Bposting&amp;utm_content=senior%2Bfrontend%2Bdeveloper%2Bm%2Bw%2Bd\">https://carl.join.com/jobs/2049948-senior-frontend-developer-m-w-d?pid=357a3b4531918760973f&amp;oid=931a7239-ba3b-4e08-bcd1-ce4c27baa804&amp;utm_source=github_jobs&amp;utm_medium=paid&amp;utm_campaign=single%2Bposting&amp;utm_content=senior%2Bfrontend%2Bdeveloper%2Bm%2Bw%2Bd</a></p>\n",
