    "description": "<ul>\n<li>\n<strong>You are</strong> working with new technologies to build excellent customer experiences</li>\n<li>\n<strong>We can</strong> build a wide range of products that are used by millions of our customers</li>\n<li>\n<strong>Together we</strong> continue to build on our technology and improve</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>See yourself in our team</strong></p>\n<p>Enterprise Services (ES) is responsible for the world leading application of technology and operations across every aspect of CommBank, from innovative product platforms for our customers to essential tools within our business. We also use technology to drive efficient and timely processing, an essential component of great customer service.</p>\n<p>Here at CommBank, we are always seeking exceptional talent to boost our many digital assets and development capability. This role will be a part of the Colonial First State (CFS) Wealth IT team.</p>\n<p>Our developers are passionate, driven, flexible and collaborative. We have an inclusive culture where you can freely share ideas in Colonial First State (CFS).</p>\n<p>We make it easy for you to learn and build on your career. We are collaborative, agile and are using the latest technologies.</p>\n<p><strong>We are interested in hearing from people who possess:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<strong>A risk mindset</strong> – all CommBank employees are expected to proactively identify and understand, openly discuss and act on current and future risks.</li>\n<li>Application Design and Development in complex software development environments.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>You are a full stack developer or a software engineer who enjoys the challenge and satisfaction of writing elegant and efficient code.</p>\n<p><strong>You are experienced in:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>C#, .Net, .Net Core</li>\n<li>SQL</li>\n<li>React</li>\n<li>Microservices architecture</li>\n<li>Restful and web API's</li>\n<li>Past experience in building secure enterprise scale applications is useful (experience in large organisations)</li>\n</ul>\n<p>If this sounds like you - apply via the link today!</p>\n",
